OL,3,CTradesman who scammed cancer patient
OL,4,Chas been jailed for over six years
OL,6,FA tradesman who scammed more than
OL,7,F#430,000 from a cancer patient to fund
OL,8,Fhis luxury lifestyle has been jailed.
OL,10,FTerry McGinlay, 44, convicted of two
OL,11,Foffences of fraud, has been sentenced
OL,12,Fto six and a half years at Carlisle
OL,13,FCrown Court on 9 September 2025.
OL,15,FThe court heard how McGinlay conned
OL,16,FCumbrian farmer David Wilson into
OL,17,Fhanding over 11 separate cheques,
OL,18,Ftotalling #432,500, between March 2019
OL,19,Fand October 2022.
