OL,6,FMcGinlay reassured Mr Wilson, who
OL,7,Fpassed away earlier this year, that he
OL,8,Fwould be repaid after a house sale in
OL,9,FIreland.
OL,11,FAn accountant's firm alerted the
OL,12,Fpolice after Mr Wilson's reluctance to
OL,13,Fprovide details of his finances.
OL,15,FProsecutor Caitlin McLachlan said of
OL,16,FMcGinlay: "The defendant had been
OL,17,Fspending money funding a luxury
OL,18,Flifestyle: designer clothing,
OL,19,Fhousehold bills were paid, holidays,
OL,20,Fdining out and a vehicle for his son."
