OL,12,Fhonour he is deeply sorry for the
OL,13,Factions that have brought him to court
OL,14,Ftoday."
OL,16,FJudge Fanning noted that he had also
OL,17,Fbought jewellery, he said: "No doubt a
OL,18,Fsignificant quantity (of the cash) on
